  "sorry for causing you too much pain, i know i was wrong",
  "I hurt you. and i know that i'm fully aware of what i've cause ",
  "You didn't deserve the distance, or the silence, or whatever shape my mistake took. You deserved more care than I gave you.",
  "You're someone who notices small things — the right temperature of a drink, the way flavors should balance especially in your favorite matcha. You bring that same attention to the people you love.",
